1. *Govorite* li engleski? (Do you speak English?)
2. Oni *govore* kako će postići napredak. (They are talking about how they will achieve progress.)
3. Ona nam je *govorila* o svojim planovima. (She was telling us about her plans.)
4. Mi ćemo *govoriti* o tome sutra. (We will talk about it tomorrow.)
5. Mi se *govorimo* preko telefona. (We talk on the phone.)